# 7. Transactions

### Q16. Transactions suddenly become slow.

Possible reasons

* Large transaction
* Lock contention
* Replication delay
* Snapshot size
* Cache pressure

---

### Q17. Why should long-running transactions be avoided?

Because

* Hold locks
* Increase cache usage
* Delay oplog truncation
* Reduce throughput

